CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 9, 1961, pg. A12, reads: "Over 500 Attend Junior Mothers' ... 'Smart Affairs of 1961'"
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Jones Kemp and Mike Malone wearing matching light colored shorts, dark shirts, hats, socks, and shoes, posing, facing each other, bending over and shaking hands, in interior with leaf patterned carpet and marble baseboards for the Junior Mothers' "Smart Affairs of 1961"
